Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.22,0:00:05.53,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,What was that? An explosion?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.97,0:00:09.54,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,This is the People's Eastern Revolutionary Front.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.54,0:00:12.04,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,We have seized control of this train.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.04,0:00:13.21,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,I repeat...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.21,0:00:18.48,Helvetica,,0,0,5,,{\fs20}People's Eastern Revolutionary Front?\NThat name sounds like they just cut and pasted a bunch of words together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.48,0:00:20.85,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,{\fs30}It’s certainly a name I’ve never heard before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:26.09,Helvetica,,0,0,5,,{\fs21}Probably just another new extremist group or something.\NThe world's really going to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.26,0:00:35.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Aren’t you going to do something about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:36.83,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.94,0:00:47.74,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,{\fs24}I-I mean, look, those guys are no match for you alone, Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.01,0:00:50.45,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.45,0:00:59.15,Helvetica,,0,0,3,,{\fs22}To try and dare to hijack a train carrying the Strong Arm Alchemist, Alex Louis Armstrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.15,0:01:04.19,Helvetica,,0,0,3,,{\fs22}You small fry, I shall teach your very bodies what misfortune awaits you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.19,0:01:08.13,Helvetica,,0,0,3,,{\fs22}Hey, you grown-ups!\NWhat the hell is wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:12.63,Helvetica,,0,0,3,,{\fs22}Didn't you hear the announcement?\NThis train now belongs to the Eastern Liberation Front!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.63,0:01:15.50,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,{\fs28}The name has changed since the last announcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.50,0:01:18.27,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,I really can’t keep up with these guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.27,0:01:21.61,Helvetica,,0,0,3,,{\fs22}Come to think of it,\Nhasn't something like this happened recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.61,0:01:22.48,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it has.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.48,0:01:24.51,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Maybe we're cursed?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.51,0:01:26.92,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Hey, you in the armor and you over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.92,0:01:30.55,Helvetica,,0,0,3,,{\fs22}Quit talking among yourselves!\NHand over your valuables quietly!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.55,0:01:31.45,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.45,0:01:36.83,Helvetica,,0,0,3,,{\fs22}You, gather up the valuables from that big guy and the armored one, and bring them over here, Shorty!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.83,0:01:39.60,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Who are you calling "shorty"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.60,0:01:41.20,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,You, obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.20,0:01:43.93,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Who else could it be? Shorty!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.93,0:01:44.50,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,{\fs26}Shorty!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.50,0:01:45.17,Helvetica,,0,0,12,,{\fs22}Shorty!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.17,0:01:45.77,Helvetica,,0,0,14,,{\fs18}Shorty!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.77,0:01:46.40,Helvetica,,0,0,16,,{\fs14}Shorty!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.40,0:01:47.07,Helvetica,,0,0,18,,{\fs10}Shorty!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.07,0:01:47.84,Helvetica,,0,0,20,,{\fs6}Shorty!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.84,0:01:51.37,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Who on earth are you calling "shorty"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.37,0:01:54.11,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Splendid, Edward Elric.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.11,0:01:56.85,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,A-An alchemist...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.75,0:02:07.89,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,How naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:11.46,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,What in the world are these people, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.46,0:02:14.50,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,As I thought, we're definitely cursed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.50,0:02:15.96,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Maybe you're just tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.96,0:02:17.13,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Huh? Tired of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.13,0:02:18.87,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,What's going on? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.11,0:02:25.11,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Of dealing with guys like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.78,0:02:28.34,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.34,0:02:32.98,Helvetica,,0,0,3,,{\fs22}Major, I'll leave the rear to you!\NIt seems like something exploded back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.98,0:02:34.48,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.15,0:02:41.59,Helvetica,,0,0,3,,{\fs22}Looks like there are some alchemists mixed in with them too,\Nso let's all watch our backs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.52,0:02:44.13,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,I'll keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:46.60,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Okay then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.36,0:02:52.83,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,2000)}Let's go!
